channel.title: Runescape Accomplishments/Goals
channel.description:
Here are some of my goals (first column is what started with, second column is current and third column is goal.
For my main (after my good main got banned i started with this) 77/77/99 Strength 1/99/99 thieving 30/79/99 firemaking Have made 20m+ from thieving and I havent started with strength Longterm goals are being maxed combat and having a couple noncombat 99s. Money and item wise to have 300m+ in items and cash including full bandos, sol, maxed mage and melee items ----Achieved 99 thieving. Not sure what to buy because everything is dropping in price
For my pure which i started about 2 days ago: not playing him much anymore 50/74/99 strength 1/1/99 range
[IMG]http://i25.tinypic.com/2z6f9j6.png[/img]
Post some of your goals and accomplishments. Use pictures if you want and no one says these have to be legit. You can use a bot if you want and post what you have got from botting.
